the three most important life skills

first important life skill how to stop
taking things
personally an unfortunate side effect of

bias towards assuming that pretty much

just because you experience something
just because something causes you to
feel a certain way
just because you care about something
doesn't mean it's about you
this is hard to remember and not just
because we're so
embedded in our brains and our own
bodies

good experiences

bad

self-righteous
